{"tid":2217143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中秋節】上海橡膠製品公司發避孕套當福利　假期後須交體驗心得","createTime":"2020-09-25T08:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T12:16:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee2c74ee10da591402220ee638ebb2d49333164","tid":2217143,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"上海有一間橡膠製品公司的員工在網上爆料，指公司發放的中秋節福利，除了月餅外，竟然有兩盒避孕套，並且要求假期過後要上交使用體驗心得。<br />\n<br />\n據網上流傳的通知文件顯示，該公司在「放假福利及要求」一欄中，特別提到「9月份入職的新夥伴有福利噢，每人將獲得一箱XXX避孕套新品」。通知稱，如果體力支持可以在國慶期間盡情發揮，「節後業務部門會和大家收集使用體驗」。爆料的員工坦言，中秋節福利送避孕套，「你讓我一單身狗怎麼整啊」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，不少網民都留言讚好，「真心喜歡，以後還會來的」、「這個公司好open啊」，又打趣稱「寫體驗？？這個公司這是想空手套黃文？」、「暗示你該談戀愛了」。有心水清的網民就認為，該些避孕套相信是公司的產品，「估計就自己家產品了，也相當於用戶測評了」、「公司產品吧哈哈哈哈」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200925/386183530067136512.jpeg/xpJE723iBQ4HVqD1WuqxFhDFA6Y1BfEcgMrwlYDK8JU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200925%2F386183530067136512.jpeg%2FxpJE723iBQ4HVqD1WuqxFhDFA6Y1BfEcgMrwlYDK8JU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=90a5796f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fac36fd65a97a1da30df9f19d03f8a613d480c18","tid":2217143,"uid":85116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"用完之後明年今日做老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca7a1ad9490141125cbda88042608db375f116b","tid":2217143,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"有咬口，吹出來的球很大"},{"pid":"3fc60d71e738ea987b6155939380042f55449e13","tid":2217143,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fac36fd65a97a1da30df9f19d03f8a613d480c18","tid":2217143,"uid":85116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"用完之後明年今日做老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"師兄你老母懷左12個月先生你呀？"},{"pid":"18d892e30605339cbbf2104bb4787a4724da1ffa","tid":2217143,"uid":85116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3fc60d71e738ea987b6155939380042f55449e13","tid":2217143,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fac36fd65a97a1da30df9f19d03f8a613d480c18","tid":2217143,"uid":85116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"用完之後明年今日做老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"師兄你老母懷左12個月先生你呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"清，你老豆老母得你出世個刻先係？"},{"pid":"1ff0a93f90275780421e09d307c5eb3dd99cc6ff","tid":2217143,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"包膠：用嚟打飛機射唔出"}]}